        "storage": {
            "value": "<p>There is a<a href=\"https://ideas.sap.com/SAPNetWeaverProcessOrchestration\"> SAP Idea Place</a> for SAP NetWeaver Process Orchestration where also BPM related ideas can be submitted.</p><h2>Include the Process Context into the &quot;Export Process Details&quot; feature in NWA</h2><p>Currently the &quot;Export Process Details&quot; function in NetWeaver Administrator only exports Process Visualization, Logs, and similar stuff, but not the actual context of the process, sub-processes and tasks. The context information would be very helpful for problem analysis and audit purposes.</p>",
